        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3968627667" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9218735280674509963">Having grown up in Perth and lived and worked in many of the places she mentioned I was utterly fascinated with this book.......Then that novelty wore off and I saw it for what it was.<br/><br/>A lump of romantic trash dressed up as historial fiction mystery.<br/><br/>I always think if you don&apos;t care if the main characters live or die you have a problem. <br/><br/>The story and characters were all as underwhelming and pathetic as each other.<br/><br/>If you are from Perth, you will probably appreciate the history, if you are not, I wo</span>
  <span id="freeText9218735280674509963" style="display:none">Having grown up in Perth and lived and worked in many of the places she mentioned I was utterly fascinated with this book.......Then that novelty wore off and I saw it for what it was.<br /><br />A lump of romantic trash dressed up as historial fiction mystery.<br /><br />I always think if you don't care if the main characters live or die you have a problem. <br /><br />The story and characters were all as underwhelming and pathetic as each other.<br /><br />If you are from Perth, you will probably appreciate the history, if you are not, I would not bother.</span>
